'''新西蘭國家廣播電台'''（{{lang-en|Radio New Zealand}}<ref>Rhiannon Hoyle.{{cite web|url=https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E6%96%B0%E8%A5%BF%E5%85%B0%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%AF%B9%E6%B8%85%E7%9C%9F%E5%AF%BA%E6%9E%AA%E5%87%BB%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E4%BD%9C%E5%87%BA%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94-11552620911|title=新西兰清真寺枪击事件死亡人数升至50人|date=2019年3月18日|publisher=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|accessdate=2020年7月3日|archive-date=2020年7月3日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703091125/https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E6%96%B0%E8%A5%BF%E5%85%B0%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%AF%B9%E6%B8%85%E7%9C%9F%E5%AF%BA%E6%9E%AA%E5%87%BB%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E4%BD%9C%E5%87%BA%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94-11552620911|dead-url=no}}</ref>；{{lang-mi|Te Reo Irirangi o Aotearoa}}），英文名称通常缩写为'''Radio NZ'''<ref name="GrundyHirst2012">{{cite book|author1=Bruce Grundy|author2=Martin Hirst|author3=Janine Little|coauthors=Mark Hayes, Greg Treadwell|title=So You Want To Be A Journalist?: Unplugged|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=_pAM9KMo0W8C&pg=PA264|date=17 September 2012|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-1-107-69282-4|pages=264–|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715123349/https://books.google.com/books?id=_pAM9KMo0W8C&pg=PA264|dead-url=no}}</ref>或者'''RNZ'''<ref name="Cissna2013">{{cite book|author=Kenneth N. Cissna|title=Applied Communication in the 21st Century|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=adP5AQAAQBAJ&pg=PT147|date=5 November 2013|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-1-136-68811-9|pages=147–|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715123355/https://books.google.com/books?id=adP5AQAAQBAJ&pg=PT147|dead-url=no}}</ref>，中文名称缩写为'''新西兰电台'''<ref name="联合国粮食及农业组织Programme2020">{{cite book|author1=联合国粮食及农业组织|author2=United Nations Environment Programme|title=2020年世界森林状况: 森林、生物多样性与人类|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OEfmDwAAQBAJ&pg=PR14|date=1 May 2020|publisher=Food & Agriculture Org.|isbn=978-92-5-132424-0|pages=14–|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715123703/https://books.google.com/books?id=OEfmDwAAQBAJ&pg=PR14|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是依據《1995年新西兰广播法》（Radio New Zealand Act 1995）成立<ref name="Statistics2010">{{cite book|author=New Zealand Department of Statistics|title=New Zealand Official Yearbook 2010|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=nshEzNPD7dQC|date=15 October 2010|publisher=David Bateman Limited, New Zealand|isbn=978-1-86953-776-0|pages=227-|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715120056/https://books.google.com/books?id=nshEzNPD7dQC|dead-url=no}}</ref>、由[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]政府資金支持的[[公共服务广播电台|公共服务广播电台]]（public-service radio broadcaster）与政府公共机构（Crown entity）<ref name="PalmerHill2002">{{cite book|author1=Geoffrey W. R. Palmer|author2=Kim Hill|title=Constitutional Conversations: Geoffrey Palmer Talks to Kim Hill on National Radio 1994-2001|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=z2kiZWxQfMQC&pg=PA333|year=2002|publisher=Victoria University Press|isbn=978-0-86473-445-7|pages=333–|access-date=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802053019/https://books.google.com/books?id=z2kiZWxQfMQC&pg=PA333|dead-url=no}}</ref>，播出新聞、時事、藝術與音樂。自2014年以来，该电台的重点一直是将RNZ从广播电台转变为[[多媒体|多媒体]]服务商，以[[音频|音频]]、[[视频|视频]]和文字形式增加其数字内容的生产<ref>Damien Venuto.{{cite web |url=http://stoppress.co.nz/blog/2014/06/radio-decline-story |title=Radio New Zealand's Paul Thompson on the decline of radio |website=StopPress.co.nz |date=June 9, 2014 |accessdate=2015-05-27 |archive-date=2015-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150421111006/http://stoppress.co.nz/blog/2014/06/radio-decline-story |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

该机构在新西兰公共广播行业扮演着中流砥柱的角色。[[新西兰议会|新西兰议会]]（New Zealand Parliament）为其[[调幅|调幅]][[网络|网络]]提供全部资金，部分用于广播议会程序。根据《[[2002年民防应急管理法|2002年民防应急管理法]]》（Civil Defence Emergency Management Act 2002），该电台在紧急情况下须发挥“保护公民生命安全的[[公用事业|公用事业]]”（lifeline utility）的[[法定|法定]]作用<ref>[http://www.legislation.govt.nz/libraries/contents/om_isapi.dll?clientID=2457045304&infobase=pal_statutes.nfo&record={6CCA2196}&hitsperheading=on&softpage=DOC Civil Defence Emergency Management Act 2002 (2002 No 30)] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120717080212/http://www.legislation.govt.nz/libraries/contents/om_isapi.dll?clientID=2457045304&infobase=pal_statutes.nfo&record=%7B6CCA2196%7D&hitsperheading=on&softpage=DOC |date=2012-07-17}}</ref>。

该电台还通过[[新西兰国际广播电台|新西兰国际广播电台]]提供国际服务，通过其[[太平洋|太平洋]][[短波|短波]]服务以[[英语|英语]]和[[太平洋语|太平洋语]]向[[南太平洋|南太平洋]]广播<ref>[http://cbc.am/Letter_PM_AU-NZ_RA-RNZI.ppt Mediumwave Broadcasting Proposal PPT] {{Wayback|url=http://cbc.am/Letter_PM_AU-NZ_RA-RNZI.ppt |date=20110813064444 }} and [http://cbc.am/Letter_PM_AU-NZ_RA-RNZI.pdf PDF] {{Wayback|url=http://cbc.am/Letter_PM_AU-NZ_RA-RNZI.pdf |date=20110813064401 }}</ref>。

2005年10月，新西兰电台RNZ网站rnz.co.nz（原radionz.co.nz）上线，包括新闻报道、节目信息、在线电台流媒体和播客。RNZ National、RNZ Concert、AM Network Parliament报道和RNZ International均以[[Windows_Media_Audio|Windows Media Audio]]流媒体形式呈现给大众。该电台几乎所有的节目都可追溯至2008年1月，并为用户提供[[MP3|MP3]]和[[Ogg|Ogg]] [[Vorbis|Vorbis]]以及下载等选项。由于版权审核不充分，有些材料无法提供。

